data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED & OFFERING $5,000 toward Rate Buydown/Closing Costs *PLUS* First Year's Flood Insurance payment! First Time Homebuyer? Snowbird Second Home? Downsizing? Come see this Gem in the Heart of Comfort! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven, complete with a 1-car attached garage, offers something truly special that sets it apart from the rest. * As you step inside, you'll find a spacious open layout! A kitchen that’s not just practical but designed with heart. Solid wood shaker cabinets, granite countertops, newer stainless-steel appliances and closet pantry ensure an organized and efficient culinary space where cooking is a delight. * Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring adds a touch of sophistication to the main living areas, while cozy bedrooms are adorned with plush carpet for your comfort. * Updates are a testament to the home's quality, including a brand-new 2023 RainSoft whole-house water conditioning system, brand-new roof in 2022, a 2021 AC unit with UV light, vinyl fence added in 2021, and an updated electric panel. * What helps make this home truly remarkable are the Hurricane/Impact Resistant Windows, boasting an impressive 175 mph wind rating. Your safety and energy savings are a priority here. * When you step into the generous backyard, a versatile canvas is ready for your imagination. Whether you envision a pool, a play area for the kids, or a peaceful retreat, this space is yours to shape. The remarkable 10 x 14 Tuff Shed, installed in 2021, with solar exterior lights, offers endless possibilities of flexible storage space for your kayaks, beach gear, or a hideaway for the perfect man-cave or she-shed. * The best part? No HOA or CDD fees, giving you the freedom to make this space truly your own. * Situated perfectly, this home is a hop, skip, and a jump from parks and nature preserves. Explore the wonders of Anclote River Park, with its beach, canoe, kayak & boat launch, fishing pier, picnic pavilions, volleyball courts, and a playground for family fun. You're also just minutes away from the J. Ben Harrill Recreation Complex and Greater Holiday Little League – offering a wide array of recreational opportunities for your family. * This is a fantastic opportunity! Be sure to explore our 3D tour for an immersive virtual experience. Your next chapter begins here - seize it today!
